0% or more in typical birds. This study provides support for the torpor-assisted migration hypothesis, and furthers our understanding of the energy budgets of migratory bats.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Baloun, Dylan E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Guglielmo, Christopher G.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1cd38274c63a7ea0d92bf612262a526e", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/ccc6bd6e6e4ec194f7cc6b40d4f0b7f42d30b6a41e0b4353c6765f8ce79b0b0a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/UU5K6SZS", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/UU5K6SZS", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/482718ac310dde77130d7737c1b77932!/b17143-19719", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "jeb.196691", "title": "Journal of Experimental Biology"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1cd38274c63a7ea0d92bf612262a526e"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:UU5K6SZS"}, {"identifier": "10.1242/jeb.196691"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "14820998"}}]}}, "title": "Energetics of migratory bats dur